data.description: Seller is offering $5,000 concessions for rate buydown or closing costs! Come tour this remodeled gem, with updated flooring, a kitchen that features granite countertops, tasteful tile backsplash, stylish tile showers in the bathrooms, fresh paint and several other upgrades. Add in the 2020 HVAC system, 2019 roof with 10 year warranty, an upgraded security system and a paid off solar array that includes a state-of-the-art Tesla Power Wall, offering the ultimate in energy savings and peace of mind in the event of power outages, and you have an exceptional home in a prime Phoenix location. Don't miss the chance to make this home your own today.
